abstract: >
  A reproducible research pipeline comparing classical and deep learning models
  for EEG-based mental workload classification. The project implements Logistic
  Regression and Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) using TensorFlow and scikit-learn,
  with Optuna-based tuning, YAML configuration, visualization tools, MNE preprocessing,
  and full Docker and CI integration.
